============================================================================
                            A L S A   T R A Y
============================================================================
  WEBSITE:  http://software.flogisoft.com/alsa-tray/
  VERSION:  0.1
  REALISED: Thu, 21 Oct 2010 23:44:37 +0200
============================================================================

  ALSA Tray provides a tray icon for setting the volume of the ALSA
  Master mixer

  Dependencies:
    * PyGTK 2.x <http://pygtk.org/>
	* pyAlsaAudio <http://pyalsaaudio.sourceforge.net/>
	* pyNotify <http://www.galago-project.org/>
	* DBus Python <http://cgit.freedesktop.org/dbus/dbus-python/>

  Usage:
    Juste run alsa-tray

  Install:
    For install ALSA Tray, run './install.sh --install' as root.

  Uninstall:
    For uninstall ALSA Tray, run 
    '/usr/share/alsa-volume-mixer/install.sh --remove' as root.

============================================================================

